        </arrangement>

        <!-- required for collection level; optional for lower levels -->
        <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">

            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>Some of the animation drawings were done for a particular project while others were
                done post-production. The collection also contains photographs, printed items
                illustrated by Pyle, as well as materials related to his time at the Disney
                Studios.</p>
        </scopecontent>

